        <updateDate>2019-08-26T22:52:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Reinforcing American-Made Products Act of</b> <b>2017</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;specifies that&nbsp;the Federal Trade Commission's regulation of the labeling of products as "Made in the U.S.A." or "Made in America"&nbsp;supersedes any conflicting state laws.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
